 EFF leader Julius Malema has responded to the
announcement by Afriforum that it plans to prosecute him. AfriForum said it wants to pursue private prosecution
against EFF leader Julius Malema on charges of fraud and corruption. Afriforum said the matter relates to Malema's Ratanang
Family Trust which allegedly benefited from the irregular awarding of a R52
million tender to On Point Engineering in Limpopo. The matter was struck off the roll in 2015 He tweeted: "Bring it on bloody racists, you don’t
scare me at all. I’m born ready! No white man will decide my destiny, the poor
masses of our people will."  